  "imageCount": 26,
  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605508107313-YIJKASP89USDB7OYYUEC/22a-scstretch.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>If you haven't signed up for my newest online class, <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/shop/classrooms/stretch-your-kit?aff=6cc2c70f\">Stretch Your Kit</a> from <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/shop/classrooms/stretch-your-kit?aff=6cc2c70f\">Studio Calico</a>, what are you waiting for? I thought it would be good to put up one last post about it before the sale ends on January 31st (tomorrow). Class begins on the 1st of February and I'll be on the message boards daily through the entire month. Remember, there are no assignments and you can work at your own pace. Plus you will have access to the PDF's (jam packed with amazing techniques and photos from myself and our fantastic contributors- trust me, their projects are a must-see!) as well as access to the videos.</p><p>We used the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/county-fair?aff=6cc2c70f\">January kit, County Fair</a> in our layouts, but the tips and techniques can be applied to any kits, your growing stash, and future projects. Included in the class are over 20 exclusive examples of layouts. Just to give you a little taste of what to expect, I did an extra layout using just the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/kissing-booth?aff=6cc2c70f\">Kissing Booth Add-On</a>.   </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"22b-dsc_05962.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605508137028-VL70W4VMADAFRGH5VJBG/22b-dsc_05962.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"22c-dsc_0597.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605508136579-9I6C68BIR444THFNW7G7/22c-dsc_0597.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22d-dsc_05981.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605508138165-8CRTRAE32KUR0JZE51PO/22d-dsc_05981.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22e-dsc_0599.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605508137906-J634VUXNLEJ7XNXG4EZI/22e-dsc_0599.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22f-dsc_06001.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605508138838-DLOOXH5DOLLLZZ63UXMU/22f-dsc_06001.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22g-dsc_0601.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605508138851-I40HQ859NKWHERYX74PF/22g-dsc_0601.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22h-dsc_06021.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605508139551-RMZLOG2EJTIC1P42ZROU/22h-dsc_06021.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22i-dsc_06031.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605508139673-P2GDOHKCJHYHNWZSNSH0/22i-dsc_06031.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22j-dsc_06041.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605508140565-31WMPFO7CJ8M8W4MD40V/22j-dsc_06041.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22k-dsc_06051.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605508141076-U45YY415548WBD3Y8E2X/22k-dsc_06051.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22l-dsc_06061.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605508141385-1MZ25W4JWAMW3Q38018K/22l-dsc_06061.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22m-dsc_06071.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605508141813-QTT6EECQ3MWDGOWU3QFC/22m-dsc_06071.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22n-dsc_0608.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605508142112-WWA2TZHKD4L67VA3VZFS/22n-dsc_0608.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22o-dsc_0609.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605508142622-5776C081CG281WC6VCY2/22o-dsc_0609.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22p-dsc_06101.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605508142802-7I3CFP13ZX3RU1L01FON/22p-dsc_06101.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22q-dsc_0613.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605508143999-EHR52CP5G8JTXUX8JMNW/22q-dsc_0613.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22r-dsc_0614.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605508144166-ZTJKUXUDJQ3XZ8WQ6DNB/22r-dsc_0614.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22s-dsc_0615.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605508145905-HRIEVE1RDALW4IZG0DQE/22s-dsc_0615.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22t-dsc_06161.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605508145907-DE7HVC4JHAEIV98ZV9JG/22t-dsc_06161.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22u-dsc_06171.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605508226759-HX7X1NVTMO2RXTVLBZ4A/22u-dsc_06171.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22v-dsc_06181.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605508225970-H9BQA7T4H84JVPCIIZBD/22v-dsc_06181.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22w-dsc_06191.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605508147360-JYIN85TYXHJERNS2X27N/22w-dsc_06191.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22x-dsc_06211.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605508259230-P5E0E91OINLXM6070GO6/22x-dsc_06211.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22y-dsc_06221.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605508148526-6ZGX7GW85NHRVSCCKQAI/22y-dsc_06221.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22z-dsc_0625.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605508148770-C2EXSQN91AMMZUR5X2Z7/22z-dsc_0625.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p><strong>In case you needed another last minute push to sign up, you can save 10% by using the code: AMYSTRETCH10.</strong>This 10% off code is valid only on the Stretch Your Kit class.  Valid through January 31st.  Code must be entered at checkout.  Refunds will not be given for missing codes or previous purchases. Please enter your code on the Confirm Order Screen in the Add Promo Code box and then click Add.  Your code will then be deducted from the class total.</p><p>Hope to see you all in the classroom soon!<strong> Let me know in the comments if you've signed up and I'll randomly choose a winner to get a fun little package from the CHA show.  (</strong>photo by <a href=\"http://www.shimelle.com/paper/1350/cha-winter-2012-amy-tangerine-sketchbook/\">Shimelle)</a></p>"
